<section class="section section-about" id="about">
  <div class="about-grid">
    <div class="about-text reveal">
      <div class="sl">About YomiType</div>
      <h2 class="sh2">不再死背五十音<br>用指尖敲擊出你的「日語腦」</h2>
      <p>你是否也曾在五十音的字表前感到挫折？反覆地抄寫、艱澀地背誦，卻總是在實際應用時候——</p>
      <p class="about-pain">～怎麼沒有辦法直接就想到發音<br>～怎麼就忘記發音了</p>
      <p>在 YomiType 練習第一步不是死背，而是「習慣」。</p>
      <p class="about-em">● 肌肉記憶優於死記硬背 ●</p>
      <div class="feature-pills">
        <div class="pill"><div class="pill-icon">⌨️</div><div><div class="pt">直覺拼音輸入</div><div class="pd">用你熟悉的羅馬拼音打出假名，讓大腦在敲擊間自動記住發音與字型。</div></div></div>
        <div class="pill"><div class="pill-icon">🎨</div><div><div class="pt">感官顏色回饋</div><div class="pd">輸入正確立即轉為深藍色加強記憶，每一次變色都是實力的累積。</div></div></div>
        <div class="pill"><div class="pill-icon">📰</div><div><div class="pt">週週更新 新聞趣事</div><div class="pd">同步日本 X/Threads 熱門話題，掌握日本社會脈動。</div></div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="about-right reveal" style="transition-delay:.15s;">
      <img class="about-illus" src="data:image/png;base64," alt="勇者">
    </div>
  </div>
